Text: Re Saturday Nightnsf Ill join you and Ill be bringing my friend charlie mike From James Sharkey To Cameron Johnson Cameron REIcom andrew Beattie Subject Saturday Night Date Tue Dec Hey guys Im getting into PDX on Saturday afternoon and Stacie I wanted to know if any of you were available to do anything Saturday night I realize the rd is very close to XMAS and there is a high probability of respective family events Regardless if you are free Stacie I are going to hit the town and would love to hang Obviously significant others or anybody else is welcome This aint no restricted affair So Stubbe you are allowed to bring your gay lover See ya Shark PS We can save the Dolphin outing for another night James Sharkey Northwestern University Evanston IL USA Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at
